data.title: Find Your New York DMV, Hours and Contact Info.
data.meta_description: New York DMV Locations listed by county and city. Find appointment, hours and contact information by DMV location.
data.text:
Find the New York DMV Office Closest to You

The New York Department of Motor Vehicles provides necessary information for motor vehicles and motor vehicle operation in the State of New York. You can find several online services and transactions available for New York motorists on their website. You may contact your local DMV or visit their website for the following information:

Traffic safety information

Traffic ticket information

Change of address or personal information requirements

Driver's license and learner's permit information

Insurance requirements

Boat and snowmobile registration requirements

And other motor-vehicle and traffic law information

Below is a list of the counties in New York along with their corresponding cities, towns and villages.

If you need to contact or visit your local DMV location, please click on your county:
